name: A First Analysis of Multipath TCP on Smartphones
tagline: Give more information about our article "A First Analysis of Multipath TCP on Smartphones" submitted at PAM 2016
body:
# What is this website?
Here you will have more information about the tools used and how we obtained the presented results.

# Measurement tools
You can have a look at [mptcptrace](https://bitbucket.org/bhesmans/mptcptrace) or at our [analysis scripts](https://github.com/multipath-tcp/mptcp-analysis-scripts).

# Get the trace
It will be soon published.

# Want to reproduce our results?
Please see [this page](http://mptcp-smartphone-thesis.github.io/PAM2016/reproduce.html) to get our detailed methodology.
